}}'''伊朗原子能组织'''（{{lang-fa|سازمان انرژی اتمی ایران}}，{{lang-en|Atomic Energy Organization of Iran }}，AEOI）是伊朗负责运营伊朗[[核動力|核能]]和[[核燃料循环|核燃料循环]]设施的主要政府机构<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.armscontrol.org/act/2014-10/features/atomic-energy-organization-iran-what-role |title=The Atomic Energy Organization of Iran: What Role?  |access-date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412105847/https://www.armscontrol.org/act/2014-10/features/atomic-energy-organization-iran-what-role |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成立於1974年。伊朗原子能组织的总部位於伊朗[[德黑兰|德黑兰]]北部的{{link-en|阿米尔阿巴德区|Amir Abad}}，並在伊朗全国各地都設有设施<ref>{{Cite web|title=Iran appoints pragmatist Salehi to head nuclear program|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/16/us-iran-nuclear-idUSBRE97F09L20130816|accessdate=17 August 2013|date=16 August 2013|publisher=Reuters|archive-date=2013-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817092615/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/16/us-iran-nuclear-idUSBRE97F09L20130816|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

